{"tid":2497005,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【被控管有多枚汽油彈，理大女生認罪、月底判刑","createTime":"2021-04-20T08:08:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T11:14:05.000Z","uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bc8461fc5827267060ae649d2cccba87e184331c","tid":2497005,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:08:34.000Z","msg":"五人被控在前年（二○一九)年十月至十一月期間，串謀用火摧毀或損毀屬於他人的財產，當中廿三歲的女學生楊泳茹承認交替控罪，即保管或控制五十九枚汽油彈、七十九瓶載有白色廢棉的玻璃瓶含柴油及畢丙醇液體等，意圖使用以摧毀或損毀他人財產，將還柙至四月三十日判刑。其餘被告鄭錦輝、丘建威、莫禮滔及黃建棋則押後至五月十四日再審，全部人還柙。<br />\n<br />\n控方形容，本案是反修例運動以來，撿獲最多汽油彈及半製成品的案件。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，前年十一月二日案發當日維園有集會活動，警察刑事情報科人員監視堅拿道西冠景樓四樓一單位，當時單位外也聞到濃烈汽油味，警察在單位外揚聲表露身份，沒有回應後破門而入。警方破門後，發現楊泳茹與另外三名人士在該單位向下層逃走，爬向樓下單位，樓下的外籍住客拒絕讓他們匿藏，他們其後在升降機大堂近防煙門被截停拘捕，警方事後在該單位中搜出多項證物，包括涉案汽油彈、玻璃瓶、及胡椒噴劑。 <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">「獨立媒體」一篇署名郭偉文的專欄文章引述消息稱，理大女生楊泳茹「因涉及1102灣仔[涉]嫌管有140枝汽油彈案件，被懲教署還柙看管近一年。泳茹向外界透露『自己被職員無理剝奪基本囚權，包括禁止她在獄內工作，無視她喝水、放風休息等的基本生理需求』，而近日更被單獨囚禁在『水飯房』，當中『無時鐘也無窗，根本無法得知過了多久，僅面四壁度日如年」，而『每天唯一與外界的交流，便是被懲教、獄內醫護輪流冷言與辱罵』。她的精神已受到嚴重困擾，有自殘表現，亦有自殺的念頭。」</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n▋文章網址： <a href=\"https://www.localpresshk.com/2021/04/molotov-cocktail/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2F2021%2F04%2Fmolotov-cocktail%2F&d=aLufatioEIfsHY%2FyaDEQJ6e24FYbdL6kC4fFNwqspTg%3D&h=511cc8c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.localpresshk.com/2021/04/molotov-cocktail/</a>"},{"pid":"ac4f33b2fc6cbb1276ceb7d753e68f15873cea05","tid":2497005,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:09:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fbca7885947f4775bacd7d47be470778283bb78","tid":2497005,"uid":223912,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:10:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/sigh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/sigh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/sigh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e55d2cc32eceecb8302a44145cfad31e5656df0","tid":2497005,"uid":223912,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:11:08.000Z","msg":"懲教狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"219e865a47b260e26cf40bacce72f040636f188f","tid":2497005,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:15:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e1b326ed1497bcbb26ce35878ccea70d5c0c620","tid":2497005,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:15:29.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"1d2de0618023b6d0870a88136590b360bf34dc98","tid":2497005,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9e55d2cc32eceecb8302a44145cfad31e5656df0","tid":2497005,"uid":223912,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:11:08.000Z","msg":"懲教狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:26:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b6346b6739f615e5dce1ed9440e3cc867d0f7c2","tid":2497005,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d2de0618023b6d0870a88136590b360bf34dc98","tid":2497005,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9e55d2cc32eceecb8302a44145cfad31e5656df0","tid":2497005,"uid":223912,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:11:08.000Z","msg":"懲教狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:26:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T11:14:05.000Z","msg":"伙走啦,柒頭"}]}